9802bb0a92c42b823fd0e894ef5694f65c8","tid":1546191,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解唔係美國國歌先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"比美帝國歌意義更大"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"唱比自己聽就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"全港連儂牆要人，文宣要人！<br />\n<br />\n8/9 美領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，全民都抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=15f0c329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"7c19d2b84ea2972443cf070bf7aceddf3582f392","tid":1546191,"uid":227405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:55:27.000Z","msg":"Ok聽你講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42bc2d6c7791ac89d367dc7d544d2205e7f85236","tid":1546191,"uid":184249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:56:44.000Z","msg":"聽完一百次 腥俾親戚朋友再聽一百次！"},{"pid":"1dd